            XTV Networks Ltd (XTV) is a publicly listed company on the Australian Securities Exchange (ASX).
        


{{businessSummary}}



General Overview


About XTV Networks
XTV build, manage, and deploy interactive online tv networks for the enterprise that increase sales & reduce costs.TV Application Services PlatformCreating your own custom, online TV network has never been easier and more rewarding. Our cloud-based platform is interactive and works across a multitude of devices and browsers proven to increase viewership of your video content.Global VideoStream video live and on-demand from across the globe. They support external sources including Youtube and LiveStream. Our client side supports HTML5 browsers on the desktop and iOS/Android tablet devices.Realtime Operating SystemTheir push networks feature low latency updating in realtime fashion. Combine feeds from Twitter, RSS syndications, and weather into your custom online television network.






Products


XTV Now
Deploy your interactive online TV network using the xTV Now HDMI device. Each device connects to your local network via Ethernet or Wifi to the TV Application Services Platform in the cloud. Highlights include:An HD-ready xTV Set Top Box connects to your HD screen.Interactive with a smartphone via the cloud.





Video Inbox
Instantly push new video content to your audience globally.Highlights include: Push video to your entire audience.Broadcast push notifications to Android and iOS devices.Interact and share content.All of your media into a single, interactive, online TV destination.





Auto Start TV
Multiply the consumption of your online TV network consumption with the xTV Windows and Mac Screen Saver replacement. Networks automatically play on laptops and PCs without sound. Connecting your smartphone via the QR code over the cloud, will turn on the sound and the interaction begins.Highlights include: Use your smartphone to interact.Drives consumption by 10-100x.






Services


Newsreader
24 x 7 Video Content Generation from your company and industry sources.





Analytics
Measure engagement, sales, leads, and learning outcomes – use your network for business outcomes and track the results.





Premium Content
Branded content from National news, Technology, Sports, Entertainment, Politics, and more where they transform your online TV network into a 24 x 7 news network for your company and/or industry.





Support
Your Turnkey online TV network is supported by our Network Operations team, based in Redwood Shores, California.






